Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:22.35,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}任何人都在迷茫中寻觅答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:42.48,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}曾以为二人同心　时间也可支配
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:50.47,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}当岁月流逝　天空不再湛蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:55.56,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心与心渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:02:03.36,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}周而复始　季节循环往复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:09.93,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}愿时光　永远停留在那瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:16.12,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}二人仍迷茫着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:25.93,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}在天边寻找各自真爱的岁月…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让任何人死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的话 就按我说得做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:42.52,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}卡嘉莉再来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反 抗 组 织？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友军…可以这么判断吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少没拿枪指着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先谈谈再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来对方也有意向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果顺利 会很有帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 这位客人看来也不是省油的灯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这方面可不太在行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你们出手相救
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们或许应该这样道谢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军第八舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛硫·拉米亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？第八舰队不是全灭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是沙漠拂晓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫赛伊伯·阿休玛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该心里有数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们救得不是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 机不可失而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是沙漠之虎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一直在做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这张脸我有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穆·拉·弗拉戈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初来乍到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩底弥翁之鹰也来沙漠转悠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来您消息灵通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军的新型特装舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被克鲁泽队一路追着逃到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-105强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军新型机动兵器的原型机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此也算认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说老实话 咱们也没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上掉下这么个扫把星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降落这里也许不是你们的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然来到这片沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听你们说说今后的行程安排
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您愿意帮我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真打算说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妨先收起枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员也下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和少尉 下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎么会在那种东西里！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…当时在曙光社里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:32.07,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an2\pos(640,610)\fs60}扎夫特军 直布罗陀基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听闻二人安全抵达直布罗陀基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚感放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的战斗辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差翘辫子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遗憾 我们未能阻击长腿和强袭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好在 你们同时降落地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长腿将成为地球驻留军的追捕目标
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段期间内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们继续留在直布罗陀基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助驻军追击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 若有机会的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能歼灭再好不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们死了回天上的心？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟驻留军那群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地面上为了找长腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起东奔西跑？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么“若有机会”？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再让我遇到它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要亲手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛伊伯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是客人 放尊重点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.39,0:09:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 还真是艰苦朴素啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只是前线基地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的窝儿在城里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了那些被烧掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔西莱 穆兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有从巴堤雅来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人全是城里最好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自个儿煮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你们帮忙隐藏舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想了解情况 赛伊伯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 让他们进帐篷没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的胜利女神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 芳名是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？既然是女神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问个大名不过分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉·尤拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们如果想去阿拉斯加…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没打算打你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是失手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后 你怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 快进去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去对面的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 你竟然坐着那种东西出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在还是地球军了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生过许多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多许多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 你怎么会在这种沙漠里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是奥布的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 说是扎夫特的势力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方你也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非整个沙漠都有军队驻守
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但三天前 维多利亚宇宙港被攻陷后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们最近势头正盛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利亚被？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非洲共同体本来就亲PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在南部顽强抵抗的南非共同体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于也被地球军抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的势力分界线每天都在变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种局势下你们还真卖力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们看来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特跟地球军都一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是外来的征服者和强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船在大气层里好使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞不了太高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻不过山脉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就等着突破直布罗陀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这几个兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那么只有花点力气穿过红海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从印度洋进入太平洋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太平洋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不确保补给手段的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法直接横渡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大洋洲联合完全在扎夫特势力圈内吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤道联合还是中立吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 性子真急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在担心那种事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴堤雅还有莱塞普号镇守呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 花点力气是指这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是达克斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 换下气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来就是为了说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我总体来说还是很亲民的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也是没法子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次多加了点夏威夷咖啡豆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己现在身在反抗组织基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 在这种沙漠里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早知道当初不该说留下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 当时坐上穿梭机的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今后会怎么样 多尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对反抗组织据点发起攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚玩过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏孩子需要有点教训
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标塔西莱 全员登机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这么晚了还在忙什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时改了着地压 现在在调整
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 原来这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你这驾驶员我省心不少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然这么有干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不做还有谁做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果不努力变强 这艘船就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉 在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来吃点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见地球军机动战士的驾驶员了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 找他什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈不上什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又忘记问他名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？原来你们不认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说认识确实算认识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉阿福梅特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加小心 这样会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您总是容易冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是熟睡的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「让他们永眠吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出警告 15分钟后进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愣着干嘛 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把话说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有完没完
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和芙蕾有话说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟基拉无关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能无关 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚在基拉屋里过夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管我什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和赛无关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都是你在缠着芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的战斗 很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再来烦我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真打起来 赛怎么可能赢得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾很体贴 她始终陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着我 说保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.84,0:21:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以来的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们谁关心过吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天边烧起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是塔西莱的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Next============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号为离开沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进驻抵抗组织基地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但巴尔菲鲁特成为沙漠中的拦路虎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天边的黑烟是战争打响的狼烟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失控的怒火无情地喷向敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮火中新的悲剧发生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达SEED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.51,0:23:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「报复」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使出你的必杀一击 高达









